<p>Welcome to Gradle 4.8.1!</p>

<p>Here are the highlights of this release:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Dependency locking</li>
  <li>Maven Publish and Ivy Publish plugins improved and marked stable</li>
  <li>Incremental annotation processing enhancements</li>
  <li>APIs to configure tasks at creation time</li>
</ul>

<p>For more details see https://docs.gradle.org/4.8.1/release-notes.html</p>

<p>$gradle
Starting a Gradle Daemon (subsequent builds will be faster)</p>

